<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink142">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>ekkar ñāḻa liṟaṅkiṇarp paṭupa</l>
<l>puḷḷiṟai kūrun tuṟaivaṉai</l>
<l>yuḷḷēṉ ṟōḻi paṭīiyareṉ kaṇṇē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
  <l>Oh friend,</l>
  <l>As the descending clusters of the Ñāḻal trees on the dunes fall,</l>
    <l>I will not think of the man from the ghat </l>
      <l>Where meat for birds is abundant.</l>
      <l>May my eyes close [in sleep].</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
